title: 10/18: Start or Sit (AFC); Trade Value Chart (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
We're welcoming T.Y. Hilton and Dalvin Cook back as we take a look at the headlines from around the NFL (1:25). Are either of these guys good starts this week? And before we get into Start or Sit let's take a look at Dave's trade chart (4:55) and find out how we're feeling about Keenan Allen, Tarik Cohen, Sony Michel, Le'Veon Bell and a few others rest of season ... A quick round of your emails (15:00) and we're debating Jared Goff vs. Kirk Cousins (21:00) before breaking down the games ...NO-BAL (26:00), TEN-LAC (36:03), HOU-JAC (42:08), CIN-KC (47:05), MIN-NYJ (50:30), DET-MIA (54:30), BUF-IND (1:00:045) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
This episode is sponsored by www.ZipRecruiter.com
